{% doc %}
  Explore Our Range — Shoppable Grid

  A placement-wide bento grid of category image-cards. Each card is a
  `spectrum_shoppable_image` metaobject: its `image` is the tile, its title is
  the card label, and its `legends` (tagged-product hotspots with x/y) are the
  coordinate pins that pop a Mini-PDP product card with variant swatches and
  add-to-cart. Reuses the Shop the Look `spectrum_tagged_product` child type.

  @param {string} mutation_handle - Mutation handle for DOM scoping (infrastructure)
  @param {string} experience_handle - Experience handle for attribution (infrastructure)
  @param {object} variant - Resolved snippet-instance variant; user-configurable values live on `variant.content`
  @param {object} mo - spectrum_snippet_instance metaobject drop; carries typed reference pools

  variant.content fields:
    - looks {object} — { refIds: string[] } metaobject handles of the cards, in order
    - section_title {string} — Heading shown above the grid
    - layout {string} — "bento" | "grid"
    - grid_columns {string} — "2" | "3" | "4" (uniform grid only)
    - cta_label {string} — per-tile hover button label
    - enable_hotspots {boolean} — render coordinate pins
    - enable_mini_pdp {boolean} — open Mini-PDP on hotspot tap (else compact card)
    - cta_text {string} — Mini-PDP add-to-cart label

  @example
  {%- comment -%} Production caller — emitted by `_sai-{instanceId}.liquid` {%- endcomment -%}
  {% render '_sai-snippet-ryi2st97',
    variant: variant,
    mo: mo,
    mutation_handle: 'mut-ryi2st97abcd1234',
    experience_handle: 'home-explore'
  %}
{% enddoc %}

{%- comment -%}
  ── Institutional Knowledge ──
  - Data model reused from Shop the Look: spectrum_shoppable_image carries
    image (the tile) + legends[] (tagged-product hotspots with x/y → product,
    full variant/price data). The legends list is both the pins and the
    Mini-PDP product list. Pool keying is by handle (== content.looks.refIds).
  - Bento layout is the Figma "Explore Our Range" 7-slot mosaic. Slots are
    assigned by card order via :nth-child — slot 1 is the large hero, slot 7
    the bottom-wide tile. Positions are baked as % of a 1200×1452 box so the
    mosaic scales at any width. ≠7 cards fall back to a uniform grid look.
  - Mini-PDP variant swatches are fetched client-side from /products/{handle}.js
    (the pool carries handle + the preselected variant only).
  - Add-to-cart goes through window.Spectrum.cart.addAndOpen (spectrum-sdk.js).
  - Colors map to theme vars; brand accent (Frido yellow #fcd00b) → --color-button.
  - Per Shopify Liquid: reference-list bracket access is broken (use
    for+offset+limit:1); comparisons only inside if-blocks; every JSON value
    piped through `json` to escape `</script>` and unsafe chars.
{%- endcomment -%}

{% stylesheet %}
  .sai-ryi2st97 {
    --sai-ryi2st97-maxw: 1200px;
    --sai-ryi2st97-gap: 16px;
    --sai-ryi2st97-radius: 16px;
    --sai-ryi2st97-fg: var(--color-foreground, #131313);
    --sai-ryi2st97-bg: var(--color-background, #ffffff);
    --sai-ryi2st97-accent: var(--color-button, #fcd00b);
    --sai-ryi2st97-accent-text: #131313;
    --sai-ryi2st97-muted: #8a8a8a;
    --sai-ryi2st97-pdp-radius: 24px;
    --sai-ryi2st97-pin-bg: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65);
    --sai-ryi2st97-pin-dot: #f7f7f7;
    --sai-ryi2st97-glow: #f5f06c;
    --sai-ryi2st97-card: #ffffff;
    --sai-ryi2st97-arrow: #307fe2;
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: var(--sai-ryi2st97-maxw);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 24px 20px;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    border-radius: 32px;
    font-family: var(--font-body-family, "Outfit", sans-serif);
    /* The section is a rounded white card (Figma 40px frame) whose background is
       the warm radial glow — yellow center fading to white end-to-end behind the
       grid — plus a soft drop shadow. */
    background: radial-gradient(
      78% 52% at 50% 45%,
      var(--sai-ryi2st97-glow) 12%,
      var(--sai-ryi2st97-card) 73%
    );
    box-shadow: 0 18px 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
  }
  .sai-ryi2st97 *,
  .sai-ryi2st97 *::before,
  .sai-ryi2st97 *::after {
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }

  .sai-ryi2st97__header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }
  .sai-ryi2st97__section-title {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: var(--font-heading-family, "Outfit", sans-serif);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: clamp(22px, 2.4vw, 28px);
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--sai-ryi2st97-fg);
  }
  @supports (background-clip: text) or (-webkit-background-clip: text) {
    .sai-ryi2st97__section-title {
      background: linear-gradient(101deg, #131313 0%, #ffe46b 100%);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      background-clip: text;
      color: transparent;
    }
  }

  /* ── Grid ── */
  .sai-ryi2st97__grid {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
  }

  /* Carousel position dots — only meaningful in the mobile carousel */
  .sai-ryi2st97__dots {
    display: none;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 6px;
    margin-top: 16px;
  }
  .sai-ryi2st97__dot {
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    border: 0;
    padding: 0;
    background: #bcbcbc;
    cursor: pointer;
    flex: none;
    transition: width 0.2s ease, height 0.2s ease, background 0.2s ease;
  }
  /* Dots shrink with distance from the active one (Figma pagination: 6px near,
     4px far). JS sets --sm on dots ≥3 away from active. */
  .sai-ryi2st97__dot--sm {
    width: 4px;
    height: 4px;
  }
  .sai-ryi2st97__dot--active {
    width: 21px;
    height: 6px;
    background: #131212;
  }

  /* Bento: % positioning baked from the 1200×1452 Figma mosaic. */
  .sai-ryi2st97[data-layout="bento"] .sai-ryi2st97__grid {
    aspect-ratio: 1200 / 1452;
  }
  .sai-ryi2st97[data-layout="bento"] .sai-ryi2st97__tile {
    position: absolute;
  }
  .sai-ryi2st97[data-layout="bento"] .sai-ryi2st97__tile:nth-child(1) {
    left: 0;
    top: 0;
    width: 64.667%;
    height: 38.567%;
  }
  .sai-ryi2st97[data-layout="bento"] .sai-ryi2st97__tile:nth-child(2) {
    left: 66%;
    top: 0;
    width: 34%;
    height: 31.680%;
  }
  .sai-ryi2st97[data-layout="bento"] .sai-ryi2st97__tile:nth-child(3) {
    left: 0;
    top: 39.669%;
    width: 35%;
    height: 27.548%;
  }
  .sai-ryi2st97[data-layout="bento"] .sai-ryi2st97__tile:nth-child(4) {
    left: 36.333%;
    top: 39.669%;
    width: 28.333%;
    height: 27.548%;
  }
  .sai-ryi2st97[data-layout="bento"] .sai-ryi2st97__tile:nth-child(5) {
    left: 66%;
    top: 32.782%;
    width: 33.333%;
    height: 34.435%;
  }
  .sai-ryi2st97[data-layout="bento"] .sai-ryi2st97__tile:nth-child(6) {
    left: 0;
    top: 68.320%;
    width: 35%;
    height: 31.680%;
  }
  .sai-ryi2st97[data-layout="bento"] .sai-ryi2st97__tile:nth-child(7) {
    left: 36.333%;
    top: 68.320%;
    width: 63.667%;
    height: 31.680%;
  }

  /* Uniform grid fallback (and bento with ≠7 cards via the --fallback flag). */
  .sai-ryi2st97[data-layout="grid"] .sai-ryi2st97__grid,
  .sai-ryi2st97--grid-fallback .sai-ryi2st97__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--sai-ryi2st97-gap);
    aspect-ratio: auto;
  }
  .sai-ryi2st97[data-layout="grid"] .sai-ryi2st97__tile,
  .sai-ryi2st97--grid-fallback .sai-ryi2st97__tile {
    position: relative;
    aspect-ratio: 4 / 3;
  }

  /* ── Tile ── */
  .sai-ryi2st97__tile {
    display: block;
    border-radius: var(--sai-ryi2st97-radius);
    overflow: hidden;
    background: #ededed;
    isolation: isolate;
  }
  .sai-ryi2st97__tile-img {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    z-index: 0;
  }
  .sai-ryi2st97__tile-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: 1;
    background: linear-gradient(
      180deg,
      rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 38%,
      rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.78) 92%
    );
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .sai-ryi2st97__tile-bar {
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    z-index: 3;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 10px;
    padding: clamp(14px, 1.6vw, 24px);
  }
  .sai-ryi2st97__tile-bar-left {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    min-width: 0;
  }
  .sai-ryi2st97__tile-label {
    margin: 0;
    color: #ffffff;
    font-family: var(--font-heading-family, "Outfit", sans-serif);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: clamp(15px, 1.5vw, 22px);
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    white-space: nowrap;
    overflow: hidden;
    text-overflow: ellipsis;
  }
  .sai-ryi2st97__tile-cta {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    padding: 9px 16px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: #131313;
    color: #ffffff;
    font-family: var(--font-heading-family, "Outfit", sans-serif);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1;
    text-decoration: none;
    white-space: nowrap;
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(4px);
    transition: opacity 0.18s ease, transform 0.18s ease;
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .sai-ryi2st97__tile:hover .sai-ryi2st97__tile-cta,
  .sai-ryi2st97__tile:focus-within .sai-ryi2st97__tile-cta {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
    pointer-events: auto;
  }
  .sai-ryi2st97__tile-arrow {
    flex: none;
    width: clamp(34px, 3vw, 40px);
    height: clamp(34px, 3vw, 40px);
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #ffffff;
    color: var(--sai-ryi2st97-arrow, #307fe2);
    border: 0;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    cursor: pointer;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: transform 0.15s ease;
  }
  .sai-ryi2st97__tile-arrow:hover {
    transform: scale(1.06);
  }
  .sai-ryi2st97__tile-arrow svg {
    width: 42%;
    height: 42%;
  }

  /* ── Hotspot pins ── */
  .sai-ryi2st97__pins {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: 2;
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .sai-ryi2st97__pin {
    position: absolute;
    left: var(--sai-x, 50%);
    top: var(--sai-y, 50%);
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 0;
    padding: 0;
    background: var(--sai-ryi2st97-pin-bg);
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    cursor: pointer;
    pointer-events: auto;
    color: currentColor;
  }
  .sai-ryi2st97__pin::after {
    content: "";
    width: 12px;
    height: 12px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--sai-ryi2st97-pin-dot);
  }
  .sai-ryi2st97__pin--active {
    background: var(--sai-ryi2st97-accent);
  }
  .sai-ryi2st97__pin--active::after {
    background: var(--sai-ryi2st97-accent-text);
  }

  /* ── Mini-PDP popup ── */
  .sai-ryi2st97__pdp-backdrop {
    /* The popup is portalled to <body> (to escape tile overflow/stacking), so it
       lives outside .sai-ryi2st97 and cannot inherit its scoped vars — redeclare
       the ones the Mini-PDP needs here, with theme-var fallbacks. */
    --sai-ryi2st97-bg: var(--color-background, #ffffff);
    --sai-ryi2st97-fg: var(--color-foreground, #131313);
    --sai-ryi2st97-accent: var(--color-button, #fcd00b);
    --sai-ryi2st97-accent-text: #131313;
    --sai-ryi2st97-muted: #8a8a8a;
    --sai-ryi2st97-pdp-radius: 24px;
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: 2147483000;
    display: none;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 16px;
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.45);
    overscroll-behavior: contain;
  }
  .sai-ryi2st97__pdp-backdrop[data-open="true"] {
    display: flex;
  }
  .sai-ryi2st97__pdp {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 618px;
    max-height: 92vh;
    overflow-y: auto;
    overscroll-behavior: contain;
    background: var(--sai-ryi2st97-bg, #ffffff);
    border-radius: var(--sai-ryi2st97-pdp-radius, 24px);
    padding: 20px;
    box-shadow: 0 24px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.28);
    font-family: var(--font-body-family, "Outfit", sans-serif);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 20px;
  }
  .sai-ryi2st97__pdp-head {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 20px;
  }
  .sai-ryi2st97__pdp-title {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: var(--font-heading-family, "Outfit", sans-serif);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 24px;
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--sai-ryi2st97-fg, #000000);
  }
  .sai-ryi2st97__pdp-close {
    flex: none;
    width: 24px;
    height: 24px;
    border: 0;
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--sai-ryi2st97-fg, #000000);
    cursor: pointer;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
  }
  .sai-ryi2st97__pdp-close svg {
    width: 18px;
    height: 18px;
  }

  /* gallery */
  .sai-ryi2st97__pdp-gallery {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 10px;
  }
  .sai-ryi2st97__pdp-thumbs {
    display: flex;
    gap: 4px;
    overflow-x: auto;
    scroll-snap-type: x mandatory;
    scrollbar-width: none;
  }
  .sai-ryi2st97__pdp-thumbs::-webkit-scrollbar {
    display: none;
  }
  .sai-ryi2st97__pdp-thumb {
    flex: 0 0 calc((100% - 8px) / 3);
    aspect-ratio: 1 / 1;
    border-radius: 16px;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: #f0f0f0;
    scroll-snap-align: start;
  }
  .sai-ryi2st97__pdp-thumb img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }
  .sai-ryi2st97__pdp-dots {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 4px;
    height: 6px;
  }
  .sai-ryi2st97__pdp-dot {
    width: 4px;
    height: 4px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    background: #bcbcbc;
    transition: width 0.2s ease, background 0.2s ease;
  }
  .sai-ryi2st97__pdp-dot--active {
    width: 14px;
    background: #141414;
  }

  /* variant selectors — bordered containers */
  .sai-ryi2st97__pdp-group {
    border: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
    border-radius: 16px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .sai-ryi2st97__pdp-group-label {
    display: block;
    padding: 10px 14px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
    font-family: var(--font-body-family, "Outfit", sans-serif);
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1;
    color: #9d9d9d;
  }
  .sai-ryi2st97__pdp-group-label b {
    color: var(--sai-ryi2st97-fg, #131313);
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .sai-ryi2st97__pdp-swatches {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 8px;
    padding: 14px;
  }
  .sai-ryi2st97__swatch {
    width: 50px;
    height: 50px;
    border-radius: 1000px;
    border: 1.25px solid #f0f0f0;
    background: transparent;
    cursor: pointer;
    padding: 4px;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .sai-ryi2st97__swatch-dot {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
  }
  .sai-ryi2st97__swatch[aria-pressed="true"] {
    border-color: var(--sai-ryi2st97-accent, #fcd00b);
    background: #fffae6;
  }
  .sai-ryi2st97__swatch[disabled] {
    opacity: 0.4;
    cursor: not-allowed;
  }
  .sai-ryi2st97__swatch--text {
    width: auto;
    min-width: 50px;
    height: 44px;
    padding: 0 16px;
    font-family: var(--font-body-family, "Outfit", sans-serif);
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--sai-ryi2st97-fg, #131313);
  }

  /* footer */
  .sai-ryi2st97__pdp-divider {
    height: 1px;
    /* Figma: 1px dashed line, 6px dash / 6px gap, #f0f0f0. A CSS dashed border
       can't fix the dash length, so paint it with a repeating gradient. */
    background: repeating-linear-gradient(to right, #f0f0f0 0 6px, transparent 6px 12px);
    border: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .sai-ryi2st97__pdp-foot {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 20px;
  }
  .sai-ryi2st97__pdp-price {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2px;
  }
  .sai-ryi2st97__pdp-price-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .sai-ryi2st97__pdp-price-now {
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 24px;
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--sai-ryi2st97-fg, #000000);
  }
  .sai-ryi2st97__pdp-price-was {
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #808080;
  }
  .sai-ryi2st97__pdp-price-strike {
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #808080;
    text-decoration: line-through;
  }
  .sai-ryi2st97__pdp-badge {
    font-family: var(--font-body-family, "Outfit", sans-serif);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1;
    color: #ffffff;
    background: #1ba94c;
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 3px 6px;
  }
  .sai-ryi2st97__pdp-tax {
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #bcbcbc;
  }
  .sai-ryi2st97__pdp-cta {
    flex: 0 0 auto;
    min-width: 279px;
    border: 0;
    border-radius: 16px;
    height: 56px;
    padding: 0 24px;
    background: var(--sai-ryi2st97-accent, #fcd00b);
    color: var(--sai-ryi2st97-accent-text, #000000);
    font-family: var(--font-heading-family, "Outfit", sans-serif);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 20px;
    cursor: pointer;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 8px;
  }
  .sai-ryi2st97__pdp-cta[data-loading="1"] {
    opacity: 0.7;
    cursor: progress;
  }
  .sai-ryi2st97__pdp-spinner {
    width: 18px;
    height: 18px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 2px solid currentColor;
    border-right-color: transparent;
    animation: sai-ryi2st97-spin 0.7s linear infinite;
  }
  @keyframes sai-ryi2st97-spin {
    to {
      transform: rotate(360deg);
    }
  }
  @keyframes sai-ryi2st97-pdp-up {
    from {
      transform: translateY(100%);
    }
    to {
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }
  @keyframes sai-ryi2st97-pdp-down {
    from {
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
    to {
      transform: translateY(100%);
    }
  }
  /* Mobile: the Mini-PDP is a bottom sheet, not a centered modal — anchored to
     the bottom edge, full-width, rounded on the top corners only, sliding up on
     open. Desktop keeps the centered all-corner-radius modal. */
  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
    .sai-ryi2st97__pdp-backdrop {
      align-items: flex-end;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .sai-ryi2st97__pdp {
      max-width: none;
      max-height: 90vh;
      border-radius: 24px 24px 0 0;
      padding: 20px 20px 32px;
      animation: sai-ryi2st97-pdp-up 0.28s cubic-bezier(0.32, 0.72, 0, 1);
    }
    .sai-ryi2st97__pdp-backdrop[data-closing="true"] .sai-ryi2st97__pdp {
      animation: sai-ryi2st97-pdp-down 0.24s cubic-bezier(0.32, 0.72, 0, 1) forwards;
    }
    .sai-ryi2st97__pdp-foot {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: stretch;
      gap: 14px;
    }
    .sai-ryi2st97__pdp-cta {
      width: 100%;
      min-width: 0;
    }
  }

  /* ── Accessibility / motion ── */
  .sai-ryi2st97__pin:focus-visible,
  .sai-ryi2st97__tile-arrow:focus-visible,
  .sai-ryi2st97__pdp-cta:focus-visible,
  .sai-ryi2st97__swatch:focus-visible {
    outline: 2px solid var(--sai-ryi2st97-accent);
    outline-offset: 2px;
  }
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .sai-ryi2st97__pdp-spinner,
    .sai-ryi2st97__pdp {
      animation: none;
    }
    .sai-ryi2st97__tile-cta,
    .sai-ryi2st97__tile-arrow {
      transition: none;
    }
  }

  /* ── Mobile: full-bleed card; bento collapses to a snap carousel ── */
  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
    .sai-ryi2st97 {
      /* Break out of any theme container so the card runs edge-to-edge. */
      width: 100vw;
      max-width: 100vw;
      margin-left: calc(50% - 50vw);
      margin-right: calc(50% - 50vw);
      border-radius: 32px;
      box-shadow: none;
    }
    .sai-ryi2st97[data-layout="bento"] .sai-ryi2st97__grid {
      aspect-ratio: auto;
      display: flex;
      gap: 12px;
      overflow-x: auto;
      scroll-snap-type: x mandatory;
      -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
      scrollbar-width: none;
    }
    .sai-ryi2st97[data-layout="bento"] .sai-ryi2st97__grid::-webkit-scrollbar {
      display: none;
    }
    .sai-ryi2st97[data-layout="bento"] .sai-ryi2st97__dots {
      display: flex;
    }
    /* :nth-child(n) matches every tile at the SAME specificity (0,4,0) as the
       desktop per-index bento rules above, so this later (in-source) override
       wins on mobile and resets the absolute mosaic geometry. A plain .tile
       selector (0,3,0) would lose to those nth-child rules and the tiles would
       keep their desktop %-widths and overlap. */
    .sai-ryi2st97[data-layout="bento"] .sai-ryi2st97__tile:nth-child(n) {
      position: relative;
      left: auto;
      top: auto;
      width: calc(100% - 24px);
      max-width: none;
      height: auto;
      aspect-ratio: 362 / 460;
      flex: 0 0 auto;
      scroll-snap-align: center;
    }
    /* Figma mobile pin: a 16px ring with a 12px white dot — reads as a white
       dot with a thin dark edge, not a heavy dark circle. */
    .sai-ryi2st97__pin {
      width: 16px;
      height: 16px;
    }
    .sai-ryi2st97__pin::after {
      width: 12px;
      height: 12px;
    }
  }

  @media screen and (min-width: 750px) {
    .sai-ryi2st97[data-layout="grid"][data-cols="2"] .sai-ryi2st97__grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
    .sai-ryi2st97[data-layout="grid"][data-cols="3"] .sai-ryi2st97__grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    }
    .sai-ryi2st97[data-layout="grid"][data-cols="4"] .sai-ryi2st97__grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    }
  }
{% endstylesheet %}

{%- liquid
  assign content = variant.content
  assign section_title = content.section_title | default: 'Explore Our Range'
  assign layout = content.layout | default: 'bento'
  assign grid_columns = content.grid_columns | default: '3'
  assign cta_label = content.cta_label | default: 'Shop Now'
  assign cta_text = content.cta_text | default: 'Add to Cart'

  if content.enable_hotspots == nil
    assign enable_hotspots = true
  else
    assign enable_hotspots = content.enable_hotspots
  endif

  if content.enable_mini_pdp == nil
    assign enable_mini_pdp = true
  else
    assign enable_mini_pdp = content.enable_mini_pdp
  endif

  assign card_handles = content.looks.refIds
  assign card_count = 0
  if card_handles
    assign card_count = card_handles.size
  endif
  assign use_grid_fallback = false
  if layout == 'bento' and card_count != 7
    assign use_grid_fallback = true
  endif
-%}

{%- if card_count > 0 -%}
<sai-ryi2st97
  class="sai-ryi2st97{% if use_grid_fallback %} sai-ryi2st97--grid-fallback{% endif %}"
  data-layout="{{ layout }}"
  data-cols="{{ grid_columns }}"
  data-hotspots="{{ enable_hotspots }}"
  data-mini-pdp="{{ enable_mini_pdp }}"
  data-cta-label="{{ cta_label | escape }}"
  data-cta-text="{{ cta_text | escape }}"
>
  {%- if section_title != blank -%}
    <header class="sai-ryi2st97__header">
      <h2 class="sai-ryi2st97__section-title">{{ section_title }}</h2>
    </header>
  {%- endif -%}

  {%- comment -%}
    Skeleton tiles — one per card handle. JS reads data-handle, looks up
    pool[handle], and hydrates the image / label / arrow / pins. A missing
    pool entry leaves the tile empty (silent-degraded: "no data yet", not an
    error — see .claude/CLAUDE.md error-handling philosophy).
  {%- endcomment -%}
  <div class="sai-ryi2st97__grid" role="list">
    {%- for handle in card_handles -%}
      <div
        class="sai-ryi2st97__tile sai-ryi2st97__tile--placeholder"
        data-handle="{{ handle }}"
        role="listitem"
      ></div>
    {%- endfor -%}
  </div>
  <div class="sai-ryi2st97__dots" data-sai-dots aria-hidden="true"></div>
</sai-ryi2st97>

{%- comment -%}
  Bespoke pool — sibling of <sai-ryi2st97>, NOT inside it (JS reads it via
  direct-children iteration on the outer instance container).

  Per card (handle): title, optional cta_url (collection link for the tile
  arrow), tile_image (the card image url), and the legends list emitted twice —
  as tagged_products[] (full variant/price data + handle for the Mini-PDP) and
  as pins[] (hotspot x/y), with tag_id tying each pin to its tagged_product.
{%- endcomment -%}
<script type="application/json" data-spectrum-snippet-pool>
{
  "cards":{
    {%- for handle in card_handles -%}
      {%- assign entry = metaobjects.spectrum_shoppable_image[handle] -%}
      {%- if entry -%}
      {%- unless forloop.first -%},{%- endunless -%}
      {{ handle | json }}:{
        "title":{{ entry.title | default: 'Explore' | json }},
        "cta_url":{{ entry.cta_url.value | json }},
        "tile_image":{{ entry.image.value | image_url: width: 1200 | json }},
        "tagged_products":[
          {%- comment -%}
            Full product/variant data for each hotspot, for the Mini-PDP. The
            legends list IS the tagged-product list — each legend carries the
            product + variant + price overrides plus its hotspot x/y.
          {%- endcomment -%}
          {%- if entry.legends != blank -%}
          {%- assign total_tags = entry.legends.value.size -%}
          {%- assign first_tag = true -%}
          {%- for i in (0..total_tags) -%}
            {%- if i >= total_tags -%}{%- break -%}{%- endif -%}
            {%- assign tagged = nil -%}
            {%- for t in entry.legends.value offset: i limit: 1 -%}
              {%- assign tagged = t -%}
            {%- endfor -%}
            {%- if tagged -%}
              {%- assign product = tagged.product.value -%}
              {%- if product -%}
                {%- unless first_tag -%},{%- endunless -%}
                {%- assign first_tag = false -%}
                {%- assign target_variant = tagged.pre_selected_variant.value | default: product.selected_or_first_available_variant -%}
                {%- assign single_variant = false -%}
                {%- if product.variants.size == 1 -%}{%- assign single_variant = true -%}{%- endif -%}
                {%- assign display_name = tagged.display_name_override.value | default: product.title -%}
                {%- assign thumb_img = tagged.thumbnail_override.value | default: product.featured_image -%}
                {%- assign thumb_url = '' -%}
                {%- if thumb_img != blank -%}
                  {%- assign thumb_url = thumb_img | image_url: width: 320 -%}
                {%- endif -%}
                {%- assign show_compare = false -%}
                {%- if target_variant.compare_at_price > target_variant.price -%}
                  {%- assign show_compare = true -%}
                {%- endif -%}
                {
                  "tag_id":{{ tagged.system.id | json }},
                  "product_id":{{ product.id | json }},
                  "handle":{{ product.handle | json }},
                  "display_name":{{ display_name | json }},
                  "thumb_url":{{ thumb_url | json }},
                  "product_url":{{ product.url | json }},
                  "single_variant":{{ single_variant | json }},
                  "variant_id":{{ target_variant.id | json }},
                  "variant_available":{{ target_variant.available | json }},
                  "variant_price":{{ target_variant.price | money | json }},
                  "variant_compare_at_price":{{ target_variant.compare_at_price | money | json }},
                  "show_compare":{{ show_compare | json }},
                  "price_override":{{ tagged.price_override.value | json }},
                  {%- comment -%}
                    Full variant matrix baked into the pool so the Mini-PDP
                    renders complete (gallery + swatches + price) on the first
                    tap — no /products/.js round-trip, no compact→full reflow.
                  {%- endcomment -%}
                  "options":{{ product.options | json }},
                  "product_images":[
                    {%- for img in product.images limit: 6 -%}
                      {%- unless forloop.first -%},{%- endunless -%}
                      {{ img | image_url: width: 600 | json }}
                    {%- endfor -%}
                  ],
                  "variants":[
                    {%- for v in product.variants -%}
                      {%- unless forloop.first -%},{%- endunless -%}
                      {%- assign vimg = '' -%}
                      {%- if v.featured_image != blank -%}
                        {%- assign vimg = v.featured_image | image_url: width: 200 -%}
                      {%- endif -%}
                      {
                        "id":{{ v.id | json }},
                        "options":{{ v.options | json }},
                        "price":{{ v.price | json }},
                        "compare_at_price":{{ v.compare_at_price | json }},
                        "available":{{ v.available | json }},
                        "featured_image":{%- if vimg != '' -%}{"src":{{ vimg | json }}}{%- else -%}null{%- endif -%}
                      }
                    {%- endfor -%}
                  ]
                }
              {%- endif -%}
            {%- endif -%}
          {%- endfor -%}
          {%- endif -%}
        ],
        "pins":[
          {%- comment -%} Same legends list as a coordinate set; tag_id ties each pin to its tagged_product. {%- endcomment -%}
          {%- if entry.legends != blank -%}
          {%- assign total_legends = entry.legends.value.size -%}
          {%- assign first_pin = true -%}
          {%- for j in (0..total_legends) -%}
            {%- if j >= total_legends -%}{%- break -%}{%- endif -%}
            {%- assign legend = nil -%}
            {%- for t in entry.legends.value offset: j limit: 1 -%}
              {%- assign legend = t -%}
            {%- endfor -%}
            {%- if legend -%}
              {%- assign legend_product = legend.product.value -%}
              {%- if legend_product -%}
                {%- unless first_pin -%},{%- endunless -%}
                {%- assign first_pin = false -%}
                {
                  "tag_id":{{ legend.system.id | json }},
                  "product_id":{{ legend_product.id | json }},
                  "hotspot_x":{{ legend.hotspot_x_position.value | json }},
                  "hotspot_y":{{ legend.hotspot_y_position.value | json }}
                }
              {%- endif -%}
            {%- endif -%}
          {%- endfor -%}
          {%- endif -%}
        ]
      }
      {%- endif -%}
    {%- endfor -%}
  }
}
</script>

<script src="{{ 'sai-snippet-ryi2st97.js' | asset_url }}" defer></script>
{%- endif -%}
